11:42.601 --> 11:44.159
Hello, you can't be in here.

11:44.203 --> 11:46.103
That's my Uncle Pat
and Aunt Jean.

11:46.138 --> 11:49.130
They like to make sure
I don't get lonely.

11:49.842 --> 11:53.300
She's not lonely. Dr. Grey and I
are very entertaining.

11:56.615 --> 12:01.552
OK, fine. They have to stay in there.
There's radiation in here.

12:03.255 --> 12:05.746
All right, let's inject dye.

12:14.834 --> 12:16.961
Is everything OK?

12:17.636 --> 12:20.161
Uh... It's fine.

12:26.846 --> 12:30.043
Owen Hunt is a murdering,
sadistic bastard.

12:30.082 --> 12:34.576
