and not my attending.

12:55.674 --> 12:57.335
Uh-huh.

12:57.376 --> 12:59.071
You disgust me.

13:01.413 --> 13:03.973
- Damn it!
- What, it wasn't good for you?

13:04.016 --> 13:07.179
- Impossible.
- It's not that it wasn't good.

13:07.219 --> 13:09.517
It's that it was.

13:12.992 --> 13:16.587
- A "thank you" would've been nice.
- You paged me?

13:16.629 --> 13:19.792
Got a 10-year-old girl with a tumor
wrapped around her aorta.

13:19.832 --> 13:22.494
- I'm putting together a team.
